OL,6,FHe adds that Reform "have since won a
OL,7,Flarge number of seats in local
OL,8,Fgovernment, led in the national
OL,9,Fopinion polls for many months and won
OL,10,Fthe only by-election of this
OL,11,Fparliament".
OL,13,F"The Greens, DUP, Plaid Cymru and UUP
OL,14,F(Ulster Unionist Party) have 13 peers
OL,15,Fbetween them, but Reform UK has none.
OL,16,FThe time has come to address the
OL,17,Fdemocratic disparity that exists in
OL,18,Fthe upper house," he said.
